site_name: St Clements Hospital, 2 Bow Road, London, E3
description: Application for Non-Material amendment to planning permission ref: PA/13/01532, Dated 20/06/2014.  Non Material amendment(s) Sought:  - changes to the general arrangement plans and elevations for the refurbishment of the adjoined North and Administration Blocks.  - An amended mix of accommodation, reducing the number of studio apartments, but the occupancy remains unchanged retention of some existing historic elements which were formerly consented for demolition. - omit two lifts.
